T1  - Domain Switch Theory: A Deeper Understanding of Transitions between Work and Nonwork Domains in Modern Work Life
AU  - Kaur, Ekonkar
AU  - Barnes, Christopher M.
AU  - Butts, Marcus M.
AU  - Gabriel, Allison S.
